WEBVTT

00:00:00.587 --> 00:00:09.395
I bow to all the seekers of Truth.

00:00:13.428 --> 00:00:20.448
Truth is everlasting and eternal
in its place.

00:00:22.117 --> 00:00:31.687
We cannot change it, nor can
we increase it.

00:00:32.766 --> 00:00:39.486
What is, will remain, it was that,
and will be that.

00:00:41.731 --> 00:00:49.673
Truth cannot be defined because

00:00:49.673 --> 00:00:57.183
unless we experience the Truth,
we cannot understand it.

00:01:00.773 --> 00:01:12.143
And those who have not sought the Truth
and those who seek only falsehood,

00:01:14.131 --> 00:01:17.171
they cannot even understand the Truth.

00:01:19.283 --> 00:01:28.513
But Truth is a very small, sparkling,
special, wonderful thing.

00:01:29.713 --> 00:01:42.393
The Truth is that we are all the Spirit.
We are not this body, intellect,
mind, ego, etc. but the Eternal Spirit.

00:01:45.441 --> 00:01:58.141
I have found a big difference between
the Indian culture or should say the
Eastern culture and the Western culture.

00:01:59.056 --> 00:02:10.366
Those who are Westerners may not even
be so aware of the Spirit.

00:02:10.858 --> 00:02:19.408
Although they believe in Jesus Christ
and Jesus Christ was born in Asia.

00:02:19.911 --> 00:02:33.514
The total perception, or the total attention of
those people, is drawn towards perishable things,
which in a moment, (UNCLEAR).

00:02:33.728 --> 00:02:42.438
But if one talks to the people of the
East, where there have been great
knowers of the principles of Vedas,

00:02:42.982 --> 00:02:52.172
seers, sages, saints, incarnations,
all of them will say that

00:02:52.333 --> 00:03:00.163
man should seek only such eternal
things, which are imperishable.

00:03:00.431 --> 00:03:04.261
And that indestructible, eternal thing
is the Spirit.

00:03:04.392 --> 00:03:12.602
Unless man seeks those things,
he cannot know the Absolute Truth.

00:03:13.693 --> 00:03:22.193
You cannot know the Absolute Truth through
the intellect. That is why the question of
all the religions has arisen today.

00:03:22.583 --> 00:03:29.573
When you apply your intellect to something,
then it goes in any direction.

00:03:29.844 --> 00:03:33.014
Every person thinks that only I am correct.

00:03:33.223 --> 00:03:41.513
The founders of every religion have
said the same thing, but their followers
think that only they are right.

00:03:42.048 --> 00:03:50.108
Similarly, in politics, some people
say that imperialism is right,

00:03:50.108 --> 00:03:55.666
Some say socialism(samvaad) is right, some
say communism is right.

00:03:55.666 --> 00:04:02.843
A number of these 'isms' and the very
meaning of these 'isms' is that it's
something we have created out of our intellect.

00:04:03.040 --> 00:04:11.420
If we have to rise above the intellect
and want to know the Truth,

00:04:11.633 --> 00:04:19.823
whether or not we have any system for
it within us, has been discussed
in every religion.

00:04:20.325 --> 00:04:32.215
But in India, because our climate
was quite good and we could live
even in the forests,

00:04:32.953 --> 00:04:36.493
thus a lot of thought has been given
to this since times immemorial.

00:04:36.755 --> 00:04:44.195
And the Sahaja Yoga I'm going to
explain to you today, is not something
new that I'm talking about.

00:04:44.649 --> 00:04:52.189
The Nathpanthis in India also
knew about this.

00:04:52.557 --> 00:05:08.387
On one hand, attention was paid to
the Vedas, etc. and the word Ved
also comes from the word Vid.

00:05:08.387 --> 00:05:13.215
Vid means to know, but not to
know through the intellect.

00:05:13.215 --> 00:05:18.025
But knowing on your Central Nervous
System, should be called Vid.

00:05:18.025 --> 00:05:24.767
Similarly, Buddha's bodh is also
to be aware. People say,
"Buddham Sharanam Gachhami."

00:05:24.767 --> 00:05:27.753
Means that the person who has attained
enlightenment is the Buddha.

00:05:27.938 --> 00:05:34.848
And all of His work was that first of
all you should attain Self-Realization.

00:05:35.208 --> 00:05:41.268
After that, in another thing,
there is a great deal of devotion
in our country.

00:05:41.268 --> 00:05:48.375
Even those who are in devotion,
there's Krishna, so even when
Krishna induced Gita,

00:05:48.375 --> 00:05:55.335
so primarily, when people worship
Krishna, they still do it blindly.

00:05:55.368 --> 00:06:09.098
Krishna has explained very well in
the Gita, but we have not been able
to read what is deep within It.

00:06:09.121 --> 00:06:17.511
For example, firstly He advised to become
Sthithapragya (a person of steady state
of consciousness). This means that you
should become a Sahaja Yogi.

00:06:17.743 --> 00:06:23.818
But how does that happen? So He said,
'Now attain knowledge.'

00:06:23.818 --> 00:06:29.538
Meaning that we should have knowledge
about our Central Nervous system.

00:06:29.538 --> 00:06:35.368
Just as we can feel hot and cold, similarly
we can understand sin and virtue.

00:06:35.564 --> 00:06:42.954
We can find out who is good, who is bad,
who is important and who is genuine/truthful.

00:06:45.210 --> 00:06:53.770
The second thing He said was,
"Whatever deed you do, leave it
to God." We just cannot do this.

00:06:53.770 --> 00:07:00.435
We can say like this for ourselves,
'Whatever actions we perform, we
leave them to God.'

00:07:00.435 --> 00:07:06.423
But this is not possible because
whatever work a person does,
there are two blessings in it.

00:07:06.423 --> 00:07:10.644
Even a father will say,
"I worked for my son."

00:07:10.644 --> 00:07:14.890
The mother will say, "I did this(spoke) for
my son, I did this for my daughter."

00:07:14.890 --> 00:07:19.101
A sense of doer-ship arises in
everyone, that I am the doer,
I am the one who does it.

00:07:19.151 --> 00:07:23.001
But when He said, 'You do the
action and leave it at My feet,'

00:07:23.001 --> 00:07:27.465
it meant that you should not feel
you are doing something, and
this can only happen

00:07:27.465 --> 00:07:32.397
when you become a tool in the hands
of God, become His instrument.

00:07:32.397 --> 00:07:38.242
Unless this happens, you cannot become
akarmi(feeling you are not the doer).

00:07:38.242 --> 00:07:40.732
So He said, let people try;

00:07:40.732 --> 00:07:43.780
When they will be tired, they will
take to Sahaja Yoga.

00:07:43.780 --> 00:07:51.808
The third thing he said, that too
very beautifully, is that, "You
give Me flowers, fruits, water."

00:07:51.808 --> 00:07:56.970
Whatever you offer Me, whether it's
flowers, fruit, or water, I'll accept it.

00:07:56.970 --> 00:08:05.413
But while giving, He has said in a very
(diplomatic) manner, that while giving,
your devotion should be matchless.

00:08:05.413 --> 00:08:09.655
Now the whole play is based on the word
'Ananya', that too is Krishna's playfulness.

00:08:09.655 --> 00:08:12.750
Ananya means when there is not the other.

00:08:12.750 --> 00:08:20.818
That can only happen when you are
united with the Supreme Being,
when you are one with Him.

00:08:20.818 --> 00:08:29.216
And it is also written everywhere
that the Power of God, the Power
of His love,

00:08:29.216 --> 00:08:37.130
moves throughout the world and
through It many tasks are accomplished
– it is written like this.

00:08:37.221 --> 00:08:41.561
It is also written that we can
have a connection with that Power.

00:08:43.108 --> 00:08:49.580
But if we doubt them, and think
that they're all lying,

00:08:49.463 --> 00:08:54.173
then My opinion is that we
have closed our brains.

00:08:54.173 --> 00:08:58.400
Whatever is written in these
scriptures is absolutely true.

00:08:58.400 --> 00:09:06.380
But because our subtle vision
is not yet open, that's why we
misunderstand it.

00:09:06.380 --> 00:09:11.522
That is why Kabir says, "How can I
explain, the whole world is blind?"

00:09:11.957 --> 00:09:15.987
Even those who seek the Truth
are deeply steeped in falsehood.

00:09:15.987 --> 00:09:23.650
And that's why today people are standing up
against religion, saying that religion is a
very bad thing and that religion causes harm.

00:09:23.650 --> 00:09:29.175
All the religions that humans have
created are based on the level of
intellect, not on the level of truth.

00:09:29.175 --> 00:09:36.871
One of its identification is that,
whether one's a Hindu, Muslim,
Christian, or whatever,

00:09:36.871 --> 00:09:41.761
they have no thought for whatever
sin they are committing.

00:09:41.761 --> 00:09:45.261
A person of any caste can commit
sin, why is that so?

00:09:45.261 --> 00:09:51.102
If he is in a caste and says that,
"I am so and so, I belong to this
religion, I belong to that religion,"

00:09:51.102 --> 00:09:55.969
then, everyone commits sins. This
means that this truth has not
been awakened within them.

00:09:55.969 --> 00:10:00.787
When this truth awakens within a
person that, "I am a religious man,"

00:10:00.787 --> 00:10:03.640
and what is called righteousness in English

00:10:03.640 --> 00:10:09.988
If that thing has happened within me,
then he can never do anything wrong.

00:10:09.988 --> 00:10:18.616
So this must be understood that this
religion which has been described
must manifest within us.

00:10:18.616 --> 00:10:23.387
Its effect must come from there.
That is why religion is in such
a predicament today.

00:10:23.387 --> 00:10:27.444
You are seeing that in every religion
there is nothing except fighting
amongst themselves.

00:10:27.444 --> 00:10:31.169
Religious people are not seen doing
any auspicious work these days.

00:10:31.169 --> 00:10:36.755
And whatever good deeds they do, they
do so in order to somehow divide
religion and then fights start again.

00:10:36.755 --> 00:10:42.310
Either you will fight amongst yourselves
or you are making the fights of two
religions into ten religions.

00:10:42.310 --> 00:10:45.078
When fighting is the work of religion,
then it's better there is no religion.

00:10:45.757 --> 00:10:52.247
So when the children of today will
see that we are just fighting like
this in the name of religion,

00:10:52.391 --> 00:10:58.531
and out of blind faith we are now running
towards it, then they will definitely
think that this is a wrong thing.

00:10:58.595 --> 00:11:05.255
Moreover, many superstitious people
are completely clutching all religions.

00:11:05.306 --> 00:11:10.386
And because of that entrapment,
the form of religion that we see
today appears distorted.

00:11:10.427 --> 00:11:15.357
Therefore, man moves away from God
and wonders if this is religion.

00:11:15.357 --> 00:11:20.314
Should this be called religion,
in which all kinds of vices,
wickedness, and money are,

00:11:20.341 --> 00:11:24.811
and all sorts of things are going on
like this. This can't be religion.

00:11:25.860 --> 00:11:36.356
But we should think — one thing is
very simple and straightforward -

00:11:37.953 --> 00:11:44.303
if we have a scriptural(shastriye)
approach, then we must open our minds

00:11:44.303 --> 00:11:50.757
and we should think that these
great people who have been and
what they have said,

00:11:50.757 --> 00:11:54.796
if we reflect about it a little,
how would it be?

00:11:55.120 --> 00:12:01.860
Now, regarding the knowledge of
Kundalini, I say that it is not
just Mine.

00:12:01.860 --> 00:12:05.608
This has been going on in our
country since times immemorial

00:12:05.708 --> 00:12:14.978
which through devotion and the Vedas,
was done and continued to be done by the
Nath sect, in a very secretive manner.

00:12:14.985 --> 00:12:19.450
As you might have heard that
Nachiketa went to King Janaka

00:12:19.450 --> 00:12:22.623
and requested him to give him
self-realization.

00:12:22.627 --> 00:12:30.170
Our human condition at that time
was such that very few flowers
had blossomed.

00:12:30.590 --> 00:12:34.559
And only one or two flowers were
going to be formed into fruits.

00:12:34.647 --> 00:12:38.127
That's why only one or two people
got self-realization.

00:12:38.127 --> 00:12:45.532
And it is said in all the religions
that a time will come when many
people will attain this thing.

00:12:45.532 --> 00:12:49.607
Muhammad Sahib has said that, "When
the time of resurrection comes" -

00:12:49.607 --> 00:12:53.556
He used to call it Kiama -
"at that time your hands will speak"

00:12:53.556 --> 00:12:59.494
"and these hands will give evidence
against you" – this is written in
many ways in the Koran.

00:12:59.494 --> 00:13:02.302
Many things we don't understand because,

00:13:02.302 --> 00:13:07.118
because how can hands speak and how
can they bear witness against you?

00:13:07.170 --> 00:13:12.400
Now, this power of Kundalini, about
which I am going to tell you,

00:13:12.400 --> 00:13:19.449
it's placed within you, it's fully
established in the triangular bone.

00:13:19.805 --> 00:13:27.595
And this is called Aasaas in the
language of Mohammad Sahab,

00:13:27.874 --> 00:13:31.740
this is what is called the Holy Ghost
in the language of Christ,

00:13:31.156 --> 00:13:36.666
and this is called Kundalini in
Sanskrit language.

00:13:37.185 --> 00:13:42.925
And that's how it's described in
Zen, and in every religion.

00:13:44.572 --> 00:13:50.412
Now, this Kundalini is called the
Holy Ghost, meaning it is a power,

00:13:50.485 --> 00:13:54.495
this is the Desire Power of God Almighty
which is reflected within us.

00:13:54.495 --> 00:13:59.387
And it is the Spirit which is the
reflection of God within us.

00:13:59.387 --> 00:14:03.729
Now, whatever I am saying, please
consider it as a concept.

00:14:03.729 --> 00:14:05.925
I have put forward a concept before you.

00:14:05.925 --> 00:14:11.219
Just like there is a hypothesis in Science,
I am presenting a hypothesis to you.

00:14:11.219 --> 00:14:18.399
Now, if you understand this concept
and can experience it,

00:14:18.567 --> 00:14:25.957
and if you're honest, you'll
surely say it's true, and then
it becomes a law/way of action.

00:14:26.374 --> 00:14:30.814
Now this Kundalini is seated
within us in the triangular bone,

00:14:30.814 --> 00:14:36.863
and this is ours, of each one of us,
personal, individual, separate Kundalini.

00:14:36.863 --> 00:14:42.966
and in it your past lives, this
life, everything is written.

00:14:42.966 --> 00:14:49.961
And She knows where you've strayed,
where you've stalled, what
mistakes you've made.

00:14:49.961 --> 00:14:57.607
And when this Kundalini awakens,
It pierces the six chakras, six

00:14:57.607 --> 00:15:07.850
the seventh chakra is beneath it,
and the seventh chakra controls
it. That, I should say,

00:15:07.850 --> 00:15:14.297
if we call the lowest chakra the
first chakra, then the limbic area
which is in our head

00:15:14.297 --> 00:15:23.419
the limbic area which is in our brain,
is called Sahastrara, and

00:15:23.419 --> 00:15:28.264
it also opens this seventh chakra.
So if the first chakra is below

00:15:28.264 --> 00:15:34.266
then it penetrates the seventh chakra,
which is the limbic area in our head.

00:15:34.266 --> 00:15:39.743
Now you will say, "Mother, why are You
talking about these old things in
modern times?"

00:15:39.743 --> 00:15:44.891
Because the modern times today,
which we think to be a big deal,
you'll be surprised

00:15:44.891 --> 00:15:52.553
that when we see abroad, we realize
that all together they are going
into a very big, ditch.

00:15:52.652 --> 00:15:58.432
Some of you must have been there,
but I've been living there for years.

00:15:59.450 --> 00:16:04.145
Now you look at the situation there
– everyone has a household too.

00:16:04.475 --> 00:16:13.405
There's no concept of home and family
among the people there. Even that is
nothing. Most of the people there
have started taking drugs.

00:16:13.405 --> 00:16:19.631
Even children there have started
taking drugs. Then there are many
dirty diseases there.

00:16:19.631 --> 00:16:28.757
In those countries where the Holy
Incarnation of Jesus Christ has
such an influence,

00:16:28.757 --> 00:16:32.915
seeing this there, the whole world
seemed like Anti-Christ

00:16:32.915 --> 00:16:36.847
How can they be said that they
follow Jesus Christ?

00:16:36.847 --> 00:16:41.576
Who even said in (UNCLEAR) that,
'Thou shalt not have adulterous eyes.'

00:16:41.576 --> 00:16:49.474
Jesus Christ who says such a thing,
'There should be purity even in the eyes,'
why are these people doing like this?

00:16:49.605 --> 00:16:55.735
Similarly, we see that among Hindus,
when it is said that everyone has
a Spirit within them,

00:16:55.862 --> 00:17:00.892
So if everyone has a Spirit,
how are you creating castes etc.?

00:17:00.892 --> 00:17:04.462
And earlier, castes etc were also
based on the tasks done.

00:17:04.462 --> 00:17:09.259
And it is clearly stated in many
[UNCLEAR - this?] that the one who
knows the Brahma is a Brahmin.

00:17:09.259 --> 00:17:12.460
So nowadays, we can even keep a Brahmin
at our place to cook food.

00:17:12.494 --> 00:17:17.194
So, can he be a Brahmin? A Brahmin
is one who has known the Brahma.

00:17:17.194 --> 00:17:23.389
Similarly, in blind faith, man
has left caste, caste which is,

00:17:23.406 --> 00:17:29.166
it has been made in such a way that
instead of keeping it on the basis of work,
it has been made on the basis of caste.

00:17:29.570 --> 00:17:36.430
The reason why this has been done is
because the way you see it in the West

00:17:36.430 --> 00:17:40.422
that people have suffered so much
loss and have had such a downfall,

00:17:40.422 --> 00:17:46.199
similarly, we see that even in the
Eastern countries there is great detriment
and we too are going towards a downfall.

00:17:46.199 --> 00:17:53.040
Even here we have many kinds of wickedness,
like the work of ghosts, sorcery etc.

00:17:53.040 --> 00:17:57.511
and many kinds of superstitions, then
the coming of gurus, and many gurus
have gone abroad.

00:17:57.511 --> 00:18:01.360
They have robbed many people,
taking money, all these pursuits
are going on.

00:18:01.360 --> 00:18:05.747
But one must know the Truth first, then
only can one recognize the falsehood.

00:18:05.747 --> 00:18:09.409
Unless you know the Truth, you
cannot recognize the untruth.

00:18:09.409 --> 00:18:13.815
So in order to know the Truth,
God has made a very beautiful
arrangement within us.

00:18:13.815 --> 00:18:19.758
This is God. His arrangement is very
well-organized and systematic.

00:18:19.758 --> 00:18:23.636
It is that, this Kundalini which is
sitting below in the triangular bone,

00:18:23.636 --> 00:18:28.898
simply by awakening It, It
pierces the Brahmarandhra,

00:18:28.898 --> 00:18:33.549
then your connection becomes one
with the All Pervading Power
spread throughout.

00:18:33.549 --> 00:18:40.974
Now you have a very strong proof of
this as well, a proof, whether there
is this Power in the Universe or not.

00:18:41.500 --> 00:18:45.350
Now you see that the height of a
human being reaches a certain limit.

00:18:45.490 --> 00:18:50.199
The height of a coconut tree goes
up to a limit.

00:18:50.199 --> 00:18:55.621
If there's some other tree, its
height reaches a certain limit.

00:18:55.621 --> 00:18:57.716
In this way if you look at the finer works,

00:18:57.716 --> 00:19:07.235
so if there's a child, then the mother of
that child, there will be a great similarity
between that child and the mother.

00:19:07.251 --> 00:19:14.280
The child of an Indian will be like
an Indian. Thousands of such acts
happen in this world.

00:19:14.280 --> 00:19:20.433
Or you think like this also,
that there's a seed, a mango
tree will grow from that seed.

00:19:20.433 --> 00:19:24.275
Many trees will grow from them,
but they will all be mango trees.

00:19:24.275 --> 00:19:31.645
Where does all this power come from,
where does all this arrangement come
from, where does it all get organized?

00:19:31.645 --> 00:19:37.398
All this arrangement is made by the
Power of God's love that is spread
throughout all the Universe.

00:19:37.551 --> 00:19:41.891
Till today we have only used the
power of hatred. Even when we
practice religion(dharma),

00:19:41.891 --> 00:19:46.193
and even when we take the name of God,
we still use the power of hatred.

00:19:46.193 --> 00:19:49.703
We have never used the power
of love till date.

00:19:49.703 --> 00:19:59.140
So this Power of Love, which is
spread everywhere and has been
working since eternity,

00:19:59.140 --> 00:20:06.793
being connected with it is Yoga.
The rest, standing on your head
and doing all sorts of exercises,

00:20:06.793 --> 00:20:10.794
and Dravidi Pranayama, these things
that are, are not yoga.

00:20:10.794 --> 00:20:16.544
In reality Yoga is our connection with
the Almighty, or the All Pervading Power
that pervades this universe.

00:20:16.544 --> 00:20:21.154
Being connected is only, you can
say to be yoga.

00:20:21.189 --> 00:20:24.315
All of you are entitled to this yoga.

00:20:24.315 --> 00:20:31.268
Now Sahaja means, 'saha' means 'with you',
'ja' means 'born', this is Kundalini.

00:20:31.268 --> 00:20:38.911
And yoga means, what I told you that,
to be connected with the Power that
pervades this universe.

00:20:38.911 --> 00:20:44.938
This is your birthright because you
are in the form of a human being.

00:20:45.110 --> 00:20:52.321
Man is superior to all the things
created in the world.

00:20:52.321 --> 00:21:01.420
What is called the epitome of evolution,
and now it just needs to achieve one
last thing,

00:21:01.420 --> 00:21:06.500
where the Kundalini awakens and pierces
to pass through the six chakras,

00:21:06.500 --> 00:21:12.607
so they become united with God.
What happens as a result of that?

00:21:12.607 --> 00:21:14.944
People will ask this that,
what is the benefit of this?

00:21:14.944 --> 00:21:20.429
Firstly, you should know that you
cannot give any money in this.

00:21:20.429 --> 00:21:25.200
This is a living work, God is
living, and His power is living.

00:21:25.200 --> 00:21:31.112
This living act, the way you put
the seed into the mother's womb,
of Mother Earth,

00:21:31.112 --> 00:21:36.736
so it flourishes on its own, similarly
this Power also flourishes on its own.

