(Paramchaitanya),

00:58:43.357 --> 00:58:52.547
He is the ocean of Grace and Mercy,
but the most of all,He is the ocean
of forgiveness.

00:58:52.924 --> 00:58:58.104
That's why any mistake you make,
He can forgive it completely.

00:58:58.723 --> 00:59:05.403
So you, with a happy mind, say
it sixteen times here

00:59:05.403 --> 00:59:13.255
that, "Shri Mataji, I am not guilty at all."
Say it sixteen times, sixteen times,
sixteen times

00:59:30.320 --> 00:59:33.610
"I'm not guilty at all, I didn't do
anything wrong."

00:59:36.334 --> 00:59:49.104
Now gather this right hand and keep
it on your forehead, keep on the
forehead, on the forehead.

00:59:49.112 --> 00:59:56.502
And press it from both sides.
Press from both sides.

00:59:56.502 --> 01:00:01.939
Just like when you have a headache,
you press it, press it from both sides.

01:00:01.939 --> 01:00:07.666
Now here you say, "Shri Mataji, I
have forgiven everyone all together."

01:00:07.666 --> 01:00:12.566
"Forgiven everyone all together."
Many people say that it's very
difficult to forgive.

01:00:12.789 --> 01:00:24.749
See, this is a wrong thing. To
forgive is difficult, and not to
forgive is difficult -

01:00:24.749 --> 01:00:30.527
Both of these things are of the
mind because you don't do anything,
whether you forgive or don't.

01:00:30.981 --> 01:00:34.631
So should know that when we
don't forgive

01:00:34.631 --> 01:00:38.398
then because of ourselves we're
playing into the hands of the
wrong people.

01:00:38.398 --> 01:00:44.662
So for everyone say it together, don't
remember anyone, don't mention anyone
by name, all together.

01:00:59.436 --> 01:01:07.266
Now the same hand, say it with your
heart, it doesn't matter how many
times, say it with your heart -

01:01:09.397 --> 01:01:14.138
and now take this hand to the
back portion of your head,

01:01:14.437 --> 01:01:19.887
and lift your head upwards, and
hold(rest) it on your hand.

01:01:20.648 --> 01:01:28.318
Here you have to say, for your
own solution, and not feeling
that you are guilty,

01:01:28.318 --> 01:01:32.581
but peacefully, understanding the
peace within, that

01:01:32.581 --> 01:01:40.979
"If we, O Supreme Consciousness! O Spirit!
If we have committed any mistake,
then You please forgive us."

01:01:41.907 --> 01:01:45.857
You can say it only once, but
say it with all your heart.

01:01:50.933 --> 01:02:01.483
Now open your right hand completely
and the place that is in its center,

01:02:02.119 --> 01:02:11.919
place that on your fontanel bone area
and bend your head, and press it firmly.

01:02:11.919 --> 01:02:18.462
Because here, open the big hole
and rotate it clockwise very
slowly, seven times.

01:02:18.787 --> 01:02:28.898
Even at this time, I respect your
freedom and I must tell you that,

01:02:28.898 --> 01:02:34.624
"Shri Mataji, please give me Self-Realization."
This cannot be forced upon you.

01:02:34.624 --> 01:02:41.496
You say it with humility seven times,
with your head bowed. Say it with bent
head. Bend your head,

01:02:41.496 --> 01:02:48.133
bend your neck forward and with bent
neck say that, "Shri Mataji, please
give me Self-Realization."

01:02:48.133 --> 01:02:54.396
Right now I'm blowing on Pranava,
and that's necessary, and you'll
see the results.

01:02:54.396 --> 01:02:59.089
How beneficial it is. There's no
magic in it, it's Pranav.

