from your fontanel bone area.

01:04:57.744 --> 01:05:00.322
See on the right hand, keep the
left hand towards Me.

01:05:04.111 --> 01:05:07.171
Now place your right hand towards
Me for the last time

01:05:07.905 --> 01:05:13.975
and see(check) with your left hand,
whether there is any cool breeze
coming from the fontanel bone area.

01:05:20.378 --> 01:05:27.878
Now, with both your hands towards
the sky, with head tilted back,

01:05:27.878 --> 01:05:33.328
ask Me a question that, "Shri Mataji,
is this the Param Chaitanya?"

01:05:33.885 --> 01:05:48.395
or "Shri Mataji, is this the love of God?"
or "Shri Mataji, is this the cool breeze
of the Holy Spirit?"

01:05:48.755 --> 01:05:54.285
You ask any question three times,
with the neck turned upwards.

01:05:56.829 --> 01:06:07.209
